Quotes on aiding patients with serious illness from political advisor Xie Ru
2012-03-10 09:19:50 GMT
BEIJING, March 10 (Xinhua) -- Following are some quotes on aiding patients with serious illness from Xie Ru, a political advisor and vice governor of China's eastern Jiangxi Province, at the annual session of the Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference National Committee on Saturday:-- China should pool both government and social resources to establish a mechanism that provide financial support or low-cost medical treatment for patients with serious diseases.-- Measures should be taken to increase the types of serious diseases eligible for free treatment, reduce patients' personal spending on medical treatment, enhance the medical skills of county-level hospitals, and encourage commercial insurers to take part in the mechanism.
